'''浪声鼓'''（{{lang-en|'''Surf drum'''}}）或称'''海洋鼓'''、'''海鼓'''（{{lang|en|'''ocean drum'''}}），是一种[[北美|北美]]的[[打击乐器|打击乐器]]，可用来模拟发出海浪的声音<ref>{{cite book |title=The joy of drumming: drums & percussion instruments from around the world |url=https://archive.org/details/joyofdrummingdru0000klow |last=Klöwer |first=Töm |page=[https://archive.org/details/joyofdrummingdru0000klow/page/45 45] |year=1997 |publisher=Binkey Kok Publications |isbn=9789074597319 }}</ref>。

==形制==
浪声鼓大小类似[[铃鼓|铃鼓]]，鼓的两面为鼓面膜，内有铁珠、豆子或石头等，以模拟海浪声<ref>{{cite book |title=Music for Special Kids: Musical Activities, Songs, Instruments and Resources |url=https://archive.org/details/musicforspecialk00ottp |last=Ott |first=Pamela |page=[https://archive.org/details/musicforspecialk00ottp/page/n103 103] |year=2011 |publisher=Jessica Kingsley Publishers |isbn=9781849058582 }}</ref>。摇动手腕以进行演奏，也可用手或[[音锤|音锤]]敲击鼓面。

